\s MBINGU NA INCHI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mbingu na inchi vinajaa utukufu wako\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ee Mungu wangu maumbile yote yashuhudia ukuu wako ee Mungu yakusifu na kukushukuru yakwabudu nginsi iwezavyo ee Mungu. \bd*
\pc \bdit T:\bdit*\bdit  Jina \bdit*\bdit la Yesu kristo ni likuu lapita majina yote mbingu na duniani. S: Jina hilo litukufu lifaalo kwabudiwa na v\bdit*\bdit iumbe vyote vilivyo mbingu na du\bdit*\bdit niani\bdit*\bdit .\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit T:\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit Ee Mungu nifunze kukukwabudu kukusifu S:\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit unifunze kukuabudu kati roho na ukweli nikiwa na roho ya shukrani ni mbele yako\bdit*\bdit .\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ndege aamukapo asubuhi ashukuru Jina Lako ee Mungu mimeya unapo ibariki yakushukuru ee Mungu wangu bahari tuitazamapo yaonesha hekima ha yako ee Mungu.\bd*
\pc \bdit T: Jina la Yesu kristo ni likuu lapita majina yote mbingu na duniani. S: Jina hilo litukufu lifaalo kwabudiwa na viumbe vyote vilivyo mbingu na duniani.  T: Ee Mungu nifunze kukukwabudu kukusifu S: unifunze kukuabudu kati roho na ukweli nikiwa na roho ya shukrani ni mbele yako.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Huzuni kwangu mimi mwana damu sijui kukuabudu ee Mungu, sijui kukusifu na kukutukuza kama vile maumbile, umenipa hakili kuliko vyote haya kwangu kuona sikwabudu.\bd*
\pc \bdit T: Jina la Yesu kristo ni likuu lapita majina yote mbingu na duniani. S: Jina hilo litukufu lifaalo kwabudiwa na viumbe vyote vilivyo mbingu na duniani.  T: Ee Mungu nifunze kukukwabudu kukusifu S: unifunze kukuabudu kati roho na ukweli nikiwa na roho ya shukrani ni mbele yako.\bdit*
